N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 600.2 - Notice of discontinuance-definitions

State Regulations

As used in this Part: (a) The term suspended or suspension shall
mean the interruption of outgoing service only. (b) The terms terminated and termination
shall mean the interruption of both outgoing and incoming service. Notes
